<msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8">
<locus from="151r"/>
<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="LIT6464Nineveh">Homily of Ephraim Syrus on the repentance of Nineveh</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘበእንተ፡ ንስሐ፡ ነነዌ፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ኤፍሬም፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በምህላ፡ ናሁ፡ ውስተ፡ ነነዌ፡ ዮናስ፡ ሰበከ፡ አይሁዳዊ፡ ማእከለ፡ ቈላፋን፡ ለሀገር፡
ጽንዕት፡ ቦአ፡ ወበግርማ፡ ቃላቲሁ፡ ሆካ።</incipit>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
</msItem>

<msItem xml:id="ms_i2.9">
<locus from="162v"/>
<title xml:lang="en" type="complete" ref="LIT6466HomilyDavid">Homily of Ephraim Syrus on king David</title>
<incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘአባ፡ ኤፍሬም፡ ድርሳን፡ በእንተ፡ ዳዊት። አኃዊነ፡ ርቱዕ፡  ብእሲ፡ በርእሱ፡ አምጣነ፡ ሀሎ፡ በሥጋሁ።</incipit>
<note>Subscription on <locus target="#171r">f. 171r</locus>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ ድርሳን፡ በእንተ፡ ዳዊት፡ ወስሕተተ፡ አንስት፡ ዘተናገረ፡ አባ፡ ኤፍሬም።</foreign></note>
<textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
</msItem>

